{"tid":2151881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（撐蘋果後續活動）12/8蘋果科金感謝祭","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T16:37:21.000Z","uid":72431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e172c4090699dec9c84fc0a0637ca148bb9acf7","tid":2151881,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBF9t0Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBF9t0Q.png&h=9143da9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始要諗聽日點延續撐蘋果活動了<br />\n<br />\n首先大家要承認紙媒已大勢已去，app先係現代人睇新聞最主要方式，大家根本就唔想買實體報紙，好難養成習慣。<br />\n<br />\n另外實體報紙其中經過過零售商轉售，會降低蘋果直接收入，所以聽日冇需要繼續勉強大家無差別式掃蘋果實體報紙，有心既都可以買比黃店、區議員派。<br />\n<br />\n所以不如直接科金比蘋果仲好，你科幾多蘋果袋幾多，對蘋果更加直接幫助,所以聽日活動為<strong>蘋果科金感謝祭</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n由買實體報紙變成網上直接科金。呼籲身邊嘅人同自己，直接科金、訂閱蘋果然後科金訂閱圖放上IG Facebook Twitter打卡加上hashtag,增加迴響<br />\n<br />\n延續活動支持蘋果，如下圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F11%2F143141_150254838fcd017cf50d258eb65837d0.png&amp;h=96a24295&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<strong>#撐蘋果日報<br />\n#SupportAppleDaily<br />\n#WeNeedAppleDaily</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>訂閱科金支持蘋果方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADamhsF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADamhsF.jpg&h=3867d2c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫屋企人訂閱<br />\n【立即訂閱：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3dmqG9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3dmqG9c&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c11d404a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3dmqG9c</a> 】<br />\n直接科金<br />\n【贊助學生免費睇蘋果：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PvsUuK&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=75a50e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK</a> 】<br />\n<br />\n壹仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMJV5fn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMJV5fn.png&h=09231738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和你撐壹週刊」計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/yhXWIXiJW2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyhXWIXiJW2&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=9574114e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/yhXWIXiJW2</a><br />\n<br />\n贈閱劵：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/hmDeG2SiVr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhmDeG2SiVr&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=aaf5ba52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/hmDeG2SiVr</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>仲有訂閱YouTube <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然 蘋果嘅youtube channel係全香港第一嘅 channel，但係仲有其他channel 都需要大家subscribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/壹週刊NEXT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E5%A3%B9%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8ANEXT&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=ec6da182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/壹週刊NEXT</a><br />\n<br />\n果籽(蘋果副刊)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCzKM7UMxGCPAgUDXmFw5Gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCCzKM7UMxGCPAgUDXmFw5Gg&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=e6002bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCzKM7UMxGCPAgUDXmFw5Gg</a><br />\n<br />\n飲食男女<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/eatravelhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Featravelhk&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=5b140d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_